title: 30 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT - Apartment & Small Space Friendly (No Equipment, No Jumping)

I wanted to leave you one of the biggest thank you comments I could ever leave. Over the last 18 months, your videos have joined me through my health journey. Gym three times a week, eating differently, and your videos daily at home/at the gym - I am down 135 pounds and type 2 diabetic FREE (diagnosed while pregnant in 2017)! The fact your videos range from beginner stages and increase in intensity over time is what helped build my confidence over time. I was able to feel good starting slow and light, and now I love challenging myself with your longer/more rep workouts. Thank you for all you have helped me achieve in the last 18 months. I felt you deserved to finally know what you have done for me!

To anyone who's reading this:
You are strong. You are beautiful. You are powerful.
Remind yourself that working out is not a punishment for what you ate, but a celebration of what your body can do!
I hope you have a fantastic day :))

i just finished this workout after not having worked out for probably 2 years now, mannn i’m sweating! my legs are shaking 😂 but i’m gonna do this every day for a month and then go back to the gym, 30 minutes flew by so fast i didn’t even blink and it was over! great stuff
